    "The proposed methodology of our Urdu NER system, illustrated through an example sentence, is shown in Fig 1.",
    "Using FastText and Floret word embeddings, the proposed system helps address various challenges of Urdu NER discussed in the previous section.",
    "These word embeddings provide contextual support among various words of a sequence, helping capture semantic and contextual information about words based on their surrounding words.",
    "This helps in addressing the challenge of words having multiple forms in different contexts by assigning the appropriate NE labels based on the neighboring words.",
